<h2>A Little Bit About Him</h2>
<p1>Ibn Al-Nafis, also known as Ala-al-Din Abu Al-Hassan Ibn Al-Nafia Al-Qurashi, was an arab physician and polymath. He was born in 1213 in the city of Damascus, which is located in present-day Syria.,</p1>

<p>Information about Ibn Al-Nafis’ family is limited, and specific details about his immediate family members are not widely documented. However, it is known that he was born into a family of Arab descent, and he was merely recognised for his remarkable work.</p1>


